Part I - FORD GO BIKE¶

by Matthew¶

Investigation Overview¶

In this investigation, I would look at the relationship between the age of the members, the duration of the bike trips, and the categorical variables.

Dataset Overview¶

The data consisted of over 100,000 records of bike trips. The attributes included the five categorical varables, as well as additional information such as the names of the stations, the latitudes and longitudes, and few others.
